README for gentoo-vdr-scripts

Version 3.0_rc1

This package contains all support scripts for vdr to make
it like a real set top box.

Dependencies:
	>=vdr-1.7.36	earlier versions are not supported
	nvram-wakeup	when being used for setting wakeup time

Authors:
	Matthias Schwarzott <zzam@gentoo.org>
	Joerg Bornkessel <hd_brummy@gentoo.org>
	Lucian Muresan <lucianm@users.sourceforge.net> ( systemd support )
	Martin Dummer <martin.dummer@gmx.net>
